HEADWORD: capacitor
<hw>ca*pac"i*tor</hw> <pr>(k⟦adot⟧*p⟦acr⟧s"⟦icr⟧*t⟦etil⟧r)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <def>a device used in electronic circuits to hold
